{"type": "article", "id": 13319, "title": "皮革味香水", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001016k1qbASPWKDC02ZYr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>有人迷恋汽油味，有人迷恋皮革味，有人迷恋橡胶味道。最近，“奇葩”气味大本营又添了一个新成员， Bottega Veneta 推出 The Luxury Travel Collection，主打独特的皮革气味，除此之外加入了独具女性香味的蔷薇，李子等气味。喜欢皮革味道的话，你可以买来尽情的吸气了。除了普通包装外还有旅行款式，目前售价 80 美元，这是购买链接。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001014thakAcSiMTpK4wN5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001015hs93CIN1Z5X0YKqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63273453\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001015gN58y0j3WbwGhdoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67716535\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001015UgHcKkAwNCvWaf2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68080808\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}